Victoria Beckham, 48, has given fans an insight into her “precious” trip with David, 47, and her family to Venice. The couple travelled to Italy via the Orient Express to celebrate Victoria’s brother, Christian, who turned 43 recently. Sharing the photographs to her 30 million followers, Victoria penned: “So special to experience the @vsoetrain with my amazing family. Family time is so precious! I love you all so much.” Victoria’s mum Jackie and sister Louise also joined them for the trip.The fashion designer modelled a selection of outfits including a floral wrap dress, a yellow midi and a strappy black maxi dress for their evening dinner on the Orient Express.